# Copy to .dev.vars for local dev (never commit .dev.vars).
# All optional. The "Should I Loop?" tool runs on its heuristic without any key.

# Option A: Cloudflare Workers AI
# Enable the AI binding in wrangler.jsonc. Optional model override:
# WORKERS_AI_MODEL=@cf/meta/llama-3.1-8b-instruct-fast

# Option B: OpenAI-hosted fallback
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# Option C: Anthropic-hosted fallback
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-3-5-haiku-latest
